===Etymology===
From late {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|sausige}}, from {{etyl|xno|en}} {{m|fro|saussiche}} (compare {{cog|nrf|saûciche}}), from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{m|la|salsīcia}} (compare {{cog|es|salchicha}}, {{cog|it|salsiccia}}), neuter plural of {{m|la|salsīcius||seasoned with salt}}, derivative of {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|salsus||salted}}, from {{m|la|sal||salt}}. More at {{l|en|salt}}.

